<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,333,936]" pageId="8" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,453,369,396]" pageId="8" pageNumber="351">Original description:</emphasis>
“più acuta e più ristretta della precedente” [shell thinner than the previous— 
<taxonomicName class="Gastropoda" family="Trochidae" genus="Gibbula" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trochida" pageId="8" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="ardens" variety="elata">
